{"tw": {"3720820": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Exploring the Big Apple", "steam_appid": 3720820, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h1>快來加入DISCORD吧！</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/extras/9f03e5b1cb6fea1fc8244286392750b5.poster.avif?t=1760712552\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/extras/9f03e5b1cb6fea1fc8244286392750b5.webm?t=1760712552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>關於此遊戲</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/extras/af25fd4b215d9f07a6f4b174c3c0c394.poster.avif?t=1760712552\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/extras/af25fd4b215d9f07a6f4b174c3c0c394.webm?t=1760712552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >艾瑪，夢想成為一名記者；派屈克，初出茅廬的軟體工程師。這對小夫妻決心在「夢想之都」紐約闖出一片天。新來乍到，他們選擇暫住在馬丁——一位專業攝影師，也是派屈克父親的老朋友——的家裡，尋求一個落腳點。然而，這座不夜城的繁華與機遇，不僅帶來了全新的開始，更將這對年輕人的感情，推向了從未探索過的未知領域……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你，是選擇大膽深入，探尋他們內心最隱秘的角落？還是甘當看客，靜觀這場人生戲劇如何上演？別忘了，選擇權，永遠在你手中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/extras/dc2e7a6beb4e001f85a90f7bd8ebf916.poster.avif?t=1760712552\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/extras/dc2e7a6beb4e001f85a90f7bd8ebf916.webm?t=1760712552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在闖蕩「夢想之都」的旅途中，你的每一個決定都舉足輕重，其產生的漣漪效應，你將在遊戲中親眼見證。每一次選擇，不僅實實在在地塑造著故事的走向，更深刻影響著艾瑪、派屈克和馬丁——這三個命運交織的人——之間那微妙又複雜的關係。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次的遊玩體驗都將是獨一無二的，不同的選擇將導向截然不同的故事線，決定著這對年輕情侶與他們房東的最終命運。你可以選擇主動出擊，引導故事發展；也可以選擇順其自然，靜看風雲變幻。這裡沒有所謂的「正確」或「錯誤」，只有讓你大呼過癮、欲罷不能的精彩體驗……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/extras/64ae15c8e82dca29d9e3f874f961882c.poster.avif?t=1760712552\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/extras/64ae15c8e82dca29d9e3f874f961882c.webm?t=1760712552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《情陷夢想都》中，你將享受到：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 超過 2600 張 1080p 超清精美繪製！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 25+ 個讓你身臨其境的沉浸式動畫！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 5+ 小時讓你欲罷不能、回味無窮的遊戲流程！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 超過18 萬字豐富細膩的故事情節！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 可互動的遊戲內影集，珍藏每個精彩瞬間！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/extras/2280253b4b9ac0130f53b7a9ba51df90.poster.avif?t=1760712552\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/extras/2280253b4b9ac0130f53b7a9ba51df90.webm?t=1760712552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/extras/a