h\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 超過 2600 張 1080p 超清精美繪製！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 25+ 個讓你身臨其境的沉浸式動畫！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 5+ 小時讓你欲罷不能、回味無窮的遊戲流程！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 超過18 萬字豐富細膩的故事情節！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 可互動的遊戲內影集，珍藏每個精彩瞬間！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/extras/2280253b4b9ac0130f53b7a9ba51df90.poster.avif?t=1760712552\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/extras/2280253b4b9ac0130f53b7a9ba51df90.webm?t=1760712552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>", "short_description": "來跟艾瑪和派屈克這對小兩口一起闖蕩紐約，翻開他們人生的嶄新篇章吧！誰知，在一位老朋友家暫住的經歷，竟意外揭開了這位老友塵封的過往，也讓他們自己的未來，變得撲朔迷離……", "supported_languages": "英文, 法文, 繁體中文, 簡體中文, 葡萄牙文 - 巴西, 俄文, 土耳其文", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/489e10c7a7a30fa933063b6003216abb3455f051/header.jpg?t=1760712552", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/a760a5e2250428e71964fa0ba707af624ce018b7/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1760712552", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/a760a5e2250428e71964fa0ba707af624ce018b7/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1760712552", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Microsoft® Windows® 7/8/8.1/10 (64bit)<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core2 Duo or better<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 2 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> DirectX 9/OpenGL 4.1 capable GPU<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> 版本：9.0<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 2 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Mac OSX 10.15 or better<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core2 Duo or better<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 2 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> Compatible OpenGLR<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 2 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "linux_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Ubuntu 12.04+ or Kernel 3.x+ based distributions<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core2 Duo or better<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 2 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> OpenGL 2.0 compatible<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 2 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "developers": ["SadPepper"], "publishers": ["FooxiedGames"], "price_overview": {"currency": "TWD", "initial": 18800, "final": 18800, "discount_percent": 0, "initial_formatted": "", "final_formatted": "NT$ 188"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "單人"}, {"id": 68, "description": "自訂音量控制"}, {"id": 74, "description": "遊玩無需快速反應"}, {"id": 79, "description": "隨時儲存"}, {"id": 23, "description": "Steam 雲端"}, {"id": 62, "description": "親友同享"}], "genres": [{"id": "1", "description": "動作"}, {"id": "25", "description": "冒險"}, {"id": "4", "description": "休閒"}, {"id": "23", "description": "獨立製作"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "2025 年 10 月 17 日"}}}}, "us": {"3720820": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Exploring the Big Apple", "steam_appid": 3720820, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h1>Join us on Discord</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/extras/2bb14659ca8ef5bebf87cef9349693d0.poster.avif?t=1760712552\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/extras/2bb14659ca8ef5bebf87cef9349693d0.webm?t=1760712552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/extras/5257703409706f9fa127aae85f791e98.poster.avif?t=1760712552\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/extras/5257703409706f9fa127aae85f791e98.webm?t=1760712552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join Emma, a to-be journalist, and Patrick, a junior software developer, as they try their luck in the Big Apple. Needing a leg up, they move in with Martin, a professional photographer and an old friend of Patrick’s father. The prospect of a fresh start in a big city pushes the couple to never-before explored spots in their relationship.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you dare to explore the deepest parts of their minds, or will you watch the play unfold from the sidelines? The choice will <i>always </i>be yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/extras/17ea2dbde3628875cbc6c152832644fe.poster.avif?t=1760712552\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/extras/17ea2dbde3628875cbc6c152832644fe.webm?t=1760712552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The decisions you make whist Exploring the Big Apple will have consequences you can see play out as the game progresses. Every pick has a tangible impact on the story and how the relationship between the unlikely trio develops.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No single playthrough will be the same, as multiple paths spell the fate of the young couple and their new host. Be proactive or stay passive – no wrong choices, only plenty of delicious fun…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/extras/1074be7f414ce71d6a55516fef9b7fbc.poster.avif?t=1760712552\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/extras/1074be7f414ce71d6a55516fef9b7fbc.webm?t=1760712552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Exploring the Big Apple, you will inevitably find:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 2600+ renders in 1080p.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● Over 25 immersive animations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 5+ hours of delectable gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● A script of over 180 thousand words.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● Interactive gallery of the in-game photo shoots.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/extras/197f1d51c33844cf49b36f17d871f12c.poster.avif?t=1760712552\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/extras/197f1d51c33844cf49b36f17d871f12c.webm?t=1760712552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/extras/5257703409706f9fa127aae85f791e98.poster.avif?t=1760712552\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/extras/5257703409706f9fa127aae85f791e98.webm?t=1760712552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join Emma, a to-be journalist, and Patrick, a junior software developer, as they try their luck in the Big Apple. Needing a leg up, they move in with Martin, a professional photographer and an old friend of Patrick’s father. The prospect of a fresh start in a big city pushes the couple to never-before explored spots in their relationship.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you dare to explore the deepest parts of their minds, or will you watch the play unfold from the sidelines? The choice will <i>always </i>be yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/extras/17ea2dbde3628875cbc6c152832644fe.poster.avif?t=1760712552\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/extras/17ea2dbde3628875cbc6c152832644fe.webm?t=1760712552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The decisions you make whist Exploring the Big Apple will have consequences you can see play out as the game progresses. Every pick has a tangible impact on the story and how the relationship between the unlikely trio develops.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No single playthrough will be the same, as multiple paths spell the fate of the young couple and their new host. Be proactive or stay passive – no wrong choices, only plenty of delicious fun…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/extras/1074be7f414ce71d6a55516fef9b7fbc.poster.avif?t=1760712552\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/extras/1074be7f414ce71d6a55516fef9b7fbc.webm?t=1760712552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Exploring the Big Apple, you will inevitably find:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 2600+ renders in 1080p.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● Over 25 immersive animations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● 5+ hours of delectable gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● A script of over 180 thousand words.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● Interactive gallery of the in-game photo shoots.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/extras/197f1d51c33844cf49b36f17d871f12c.poster.avif?t=1760712552\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/extras/197f1d51c33844cf49b36f17d871f12c.webm?t=1760712552\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>", "short_description": "Follow Emma and Patrick – a young married couple – on their adventure as they move to New York to start a new chapter in their lives. A temporary stay at an old friend’s soon reveals a lot about his past and their future…", "supported_languages": "English, French, Traditional Chinese, Simplified Chinese, Portuguese - Brazil, Russian, Turkish", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/489e10c7a7a30fa933063b6003216abb3455f051/header.jpg?t=1760712552", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/a760a5e2250428e71964fa0ba707af624ce018b7/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1760712552", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3720820/a760a5e2250428e71964fa0ba707af624ce018b7/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1760712552", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><st